  "concept": "vuejs/core#9445: Playground warning while running SSR ",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:23:31.587157+00:00",
  "text": "Playground warning while running SSR \n\n### Vue version\n\n3.3.6\n\n### Link to minimal reproduction\n\nhttps://deploy-preview-9442--vue-sfc-playground.netlify.app/#__SSR__\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nOpen the link\n\n### What is expected?\n\nNot to warn\n\n### What is actually happening?\n\nIs warning \r\n![image](https://github.com/vuejs/core/assets/4620458/0aca9f92-f419-4e45-8255-c5411b7e71d6)\r\n\n\n### System Info\n\n_No response_\n\n### Any additional comments?\n\n[Explanation here](https://github.com/vuejs/core/pull/9442#issuecomment-1772374070)\r\n\r\n> This is a playground problem, there is no problem locally. This is probably because runtime and ssr use the same currentInstance in the playground.",
  "language": "en",
